resolution: Accepted storage-format ADR; explicit pm_format_version remains implicit at baseline and gates future migrations through health/validate.
expected_result: "Storage schema evolution has a documented, token-efficient per-item version gate without serializing baseline metadata."
actual_result: docs/ARCHITECTURE.md documents the contract; linked health and validate commands passed in tracker context.
